                                                              Riki the Sneaky Demon
 Starting stats 4 strenght, 10 agility, 5 inteillgence, Stats gain per level, 0.30 Strenght, 1.10 Agility, 0.40 Inteillgence.
 Base movespeed 305, Base attack damage 4-6, Base Regeneration Health 0.8, Base Regeneration Mana 0.5.


LEVEL 30 TALENT

talent 1
increase Riki health by 175 and his armor by 7
Riki will gain 1% evasion for every 85 health missing and also gaining 0.3 health regeneration for every 60 health missing, Smoke
Grenade will give allys 5 plus 10% of riki Agility in health regeneration to them and also reducing all incoming damage while in the
Smoke Grenade by 12%, also reduce Smoke Grenade coldown by 2 and mana cost by 75

talent 2
Increase Riki agility by 10 and his Inteillgence by 14
Riki will gain 30% of his Inteillgence into bonus agility and every 1 point of agility will give Riki 4 mana and further increase the
attack speed gain from agility by 0.40, Riki Dagger Strike and Blink Strike will have 15% coldown reduction and have 40% of Riki Agility
in bonus damage, they will also reduce all healing source on the enemys target by 12% for 9 seconds

PASSIVE F OR D Demon Skin
increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF Riki will gain 3 health per agility he got, he also gain 1 damage for every 4 agility he got instead of 5, he also start with 10%
evasion, 100 health and 3 Armor, his Basic Spells will do 50% of his total Evasion into damage bonus, he also reduce all slowing effect
duration by 30% and he start with a Special dagger that cannot be change, he can also have 1 more dagger into his right or left hand.
DEBUFF riki only gain 1 life per strenght and he take 125% more damage from pure,magical,physical also he can only use dagger weapons type
he also lose 35% of his max mana and spell vamp wont have any effect on riki spell and any pure damage type will do 2.5% of riki health
as damage bonus and he cannot have any Critical chance and Critical damage at all - only from Roktoru dagger -

Roktoru Dagger Special
increase base damage by 3 increase by 1 for every 3 level
increase Agility by 5 increase by 1 for every 2 levels
Physical spell crit chance 10% increase by 1% for every 10 level
Physical spell crit damage 120% increase by 1% for every 2 level
can also be use to deal 100% crit for a 1 time use with any spell of riki spell having 10% more crit damage as well
cooldown of 60 second

Roktoru dagger can be Upgraded at level 40 with special material, these are the following bonus stats when upgraded.
increase base damage bonus by 12
increase Agility bonus by 16
increase Attack speed by 45
increase Evasion by 10%
Riki Basic attacks will also crit for the same amount on Roktoru Dagger.
give 40% chance to True Strike, Ignoring Evasion and dealing 75% of Riki Agility in Pure damage
(Stack with Demon Blood True Strike Having 65% chance of True Strike

talent level 40 upgrade Demon Blood
Riki will Become Immune to all Rooting effects and if any spells are Roots casted on Riki, he will gain 50% increase attack damage for
10 seconds (doesnt have a coldown), Riki also gain 4 More health from Agility and also gaining 2 mana per Agility and Strenght, Riki
will do 35% bonus Damage on enemys below 40% health with his Spells and Auto attacks, he also give his Basic Spell 35% of his agility
into bonus damage for them, Riki will have 25% chance True Strike, Ignoring Evasion and dealing 75% of Agility in Pure damage,
taking this Passive talent will Disable all Other True Strike effect (not from Roktoru Dagger)


