add a new modifier Vampiric Blink
Riki will gain 10% Lifesteal on Blink Strike and his Auto Attack, 50% of that Lifesteal done will be bonus health for riki up to 400
bonus health max, at 150 health bonus Riki will gain 10% lifesteal with his Auto Attack and 25 attack speed, at 325 Health bonus Riki
will gain 8% evasion with 135 mana and 4.2 health regeneration, Riki will lose 15 stacks every time he get lifesteal or Spellvamp from
enemys, he will lose 50% of his bonus on Death, Blink Stab will also Jump on 3 Other units for 50% of its damage and BackStab Agility
Strike Damage, Blink Strike will slow the target by 1% for every 25 health they lose from Blink Strike for 4 seconds.

SPELL E Smoke Grenade
Throw a smoke at the target location dealing small amount of damage and causing enemy to miss and get slow also increase ally magic resist.
The smoke will have 0.1 increase duration for every 5 point of agility riki got.

