add a new modifier Snake Poison Smoke -color of the Smoke will become green purple mix-
Riki Smoke will deal 15% of his attack damage every 0.4 seconds in Pure damage, they will also take 2% increase damage from it
the longer they stand in it, the debuff will last 1.2 seconds after they leave it (if they enter again it will refresh it again),
the enemys will also have 8% chance to be stun for 0.5 seconds from the Smoke every time they take damage from it, enemys will take 25%
more damage from Riki spell and attacks when they stand in it, Riki will be Invisible in Smoke Grenade, he will become Invis again if
he attack or cast any spell after 1.4 seconds.


PASSIVE D OR F BackStab -NOTE- this affect only work behind that mean if riki attack from the front once the target 2 stacks
increase riki agility and his attack speed, Riki will deal bonus damage behind his target base on his Agility, each time he strike
that target in his back, he will reduce their armor every time up to 7 8 9 10 stack of reduce armor to them, at max stack the enemys
will take Pure damage from Riki total basic attacks damage and be stun for 1 seconds, Enemys cannot be stun again for 10 seconds.

